name: #1 - Into Her Eye
description:
This is my debut in HEN. This digitalized analog collagework is one of my studies about the collage techniques based in the Neo-concrete style and pop art.  
The mystery of the eye in the image makes you think about what's inside her mind, forms and warm colors reminding the vivacity of the 80's.
But...what mind ?

- Kejo, Brazil.
